    <h2>1. What does Rishab do when Rithika is annoyed?</h2>
    <div class="options">
      <button onclick="lockAnswer(this)">Stop paying attention</button>
      <button onclick="lockAnswer(this)">Keep cutting her when she is talking</button>
      <button onclick="lockAnswer(this)">Call her mean</button>
      <button onclick="lockAnswer(this)">Not giving her attention when she is bored</button>
    </div>
  </div>

